snippet: A day after 18 seeds fell by the wayside at Wimbledon, Stan Wawrinka was under no illusions about why he joined the list on Friday -- he had fallen victim to a serious bout of "hesitation"....
lead_paragraph: A day after 18 seeds fell by the wayside at Wimbledon, Stan Wawrinka was under no illusions about why he joined the list on Friday -- he had fallen victim to a serious bout of "hesitation".

headline.print_headline: Caution Condemns Wawrinka to Seeds' Scrapheap
headline.main: Caution Condemns Wawrinka to Seeds' Scrapheap
